properties.headline: FLOODING WEEMELAH TO GARAH Carnarvon Highway
properties.otherAdvice: Use caution travelling between Mungindi and Weemalah and between Moree and Garah as there is water over the road in sections.
properties.diversions:
A suitable diversion for all vehicles is available via Boombi:

Eastbound: from Mungindi take the Caloona Boombi Rd to Boombi, then Boonangar Rd to Garah.

Westbound: Boonangar Rd to Boombi then Caloona Boombi Rd to Mungindi.

Boonangar Rd is open, but may have damaged to the road surface and water over the road in some sections

properties.headline: FLOODING WALGETT TO BREWARRINA Kamilaroi Highway
properties.otherAdvice: The road is flooded approximately 65km west of Walgett.
properties.diversions:
From Brewarrina: Kamilaroi Hwy to Bourke, Mitchell Hwy to Nevertire, Oxley Hwy to Gilgandra and Castlereagh Hwy to Walgett.

From Walgett: Castlereagh Hwy to Gilgandra, Oxley Hwy to Nevertire, Mitchell Hwy to Bourke and Kamilaroi Hwy to Brewarrina.

This diversion is suitable for all vehicles.

properties.headline: FLOODING COBAR TO BOURKE Kidman Way between Barrier Highway and Mitchell Highway
properties.otherAdvice: The road is still open to heavy vehicles.
properties.diversions: Light vehicles can use the Barrier Hwy and Mitchell Hwy.

properties.headline: FLOODING WILCANNIA TO IVANHOE Cobb Highway CLOSED
properties.diversions:
Southbound from Wilcannia: Barrier Hwy to Cobar, Kidman Way to Goolgowi, and Mid Western Hwy to Hay.

Northbound from Hay: Mid Western Hwy to Goolgowi, Kidman Way to Cobar, and Barrier Hwy to Wilcannia.

This route is suitable for all vehicles and will add around 4hrs to your travel time.

properties.headline: FLOODING ROYAL NATIONAL PARK Audley Weir is closed between Audley Road and Sir Bertram Stevens Drive
properties.otherAdvice: Visitors are encouraged to check the Royal National Park local alerts before travelling for updates on precinct access.
properties.diversions:
Access to/from the Royal National Park is available via Waterfall: Princes Hwy, McKell Av and Sir Bertram Stevens Dr.

From Stanwell Tops: Lawrence Hargrave Dr, Otford Rd, Lady Wakehurst Dr, to access Sir Bertram Stevens Dr.
